Package: animalsounds
Title: Tells You Animal Noises, Then Insults You Mildly
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ed", "Donnellan", , "ed.donnellan@warwick.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2739-7322"))
Description: Takes an animal and a description of a noise as an input. Prints it in a sentence, along with a randomly selected mild insult.
